OL,5,G0900 Martin Clunes: Islands of America
OL,6,     FMartin heads to the lush and
OL,7,     Ftropical islands of Hawaii for a
OL,8,     Flook beyond its image as a tourist
OL,9,     Fparadise, and into the havoc
OL,10,     Fwreaked by advancing lava fields
OL,11,     Fand smoking craters.
OL,12,G1000 Martin Clunes: Islands of America
OL,13,     FStarting at Washington's San Juan
OL,14,     FIslands, Martin heads to
OL,15,     FCalifornia's Channel Islands. He
OL,16,     Fcrosses 2,000 miles to Avery
OL,17,     FIsland, witnessing Louisiana's
OL,18,     Fdisappearing coastal communities.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
